    "category": "Animation",
    "description": {
      "zh-Hans": "按顺序播放多个时间段的动画，每个时间段输出不同的值序列。类似 DAW 编排器，支持循环播放和段间过渡混合。",
      "en": "Plays multiple timed animation segments in sequence, each with its own value curve. Like a DAW-style sequencer with loop and cross-fade support."
    },
    "tags": ["animation", "sequencer"],
    "author": "BuiltIn",
    "version": "1.0"
  },
